                                  User Stories

1. As a priest, I want to be able to change the order of the songs for each service.
2. As a priest, I want to be able to search through the sermons
3. As a priest, I want to be able to print the schedule for songs that will be sung this service, in order.
4. As a church goer, I want to be able to see the current sermons that is been sung at the service.
5. As a church goer, I want to be able to access the options menu.
6. As A church goer, I want to be able to donate to the church through paypal at the push of button.
7. As A church goer, I want to be able to connect to a external device to get today sermons.
8. As a church goer, I want to be able to access songs and sermons from previous and upcoming days.
9. As a church goer, I want to be able to edit appearance of application. (Instead of images, only plain text).
10. As a church goer, I want to highlight my favorite songs.
11. As an administrator or priest, I want to be able to add songs to the database.
12. As an administrator or priest, I want to be able to edit songs in the database.
13. As an priest, I want to be able to see the length of the song in the database.
